Underfoot, a translucent rubber cage overlays the full-length Boost midsole, which offers cushioning. The shoe's release was exclusive to Europe, Africa, India, the Middle East, Russia, Ukraine and China.

The Air Jordan 4 Retro OG 'Bred' 2019 released to help celebrate the 30th annivesary of the silhouette. Featuring the same OG colorway that Michael Jordan wore while hitting 'The Shot' in 1989, the shoe features a black nubuck upper complemented by hits of Cement Grey. Fire Red accents emerge on the tongue and outsole, while Air in the heel provides cushioning.

The Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG GS ‘Bleached Coral’ is a big kid’s shoe delivered in a pastel colorway with heritage accents. Cracked black leather on the forefoot overlay and eyestay contrasts against white leather and pink suede on the upper. Underfoot, comfortable strides are delivered by the traditional rubber cupsole with an Air-sole unit in the heel. The ventilated tongue is adorned by a Nike Air tag and the back tab displays the Wings logo.

shoeName: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY White
description: A collaboration between Converse and Comme des Garçons founder Rei Kawakubo, the Comme des Garçons x Chuck 70 Ox 'Play' features a look designed by graphic artist Filip Pagowski. The shoe's Milk upper is built with canvas, accented by an oversized heart design on the quarter panel. Underfoot, a classic vulcanized midsole supports the fit.

shoeName: Nike Kyrie Flytrap V Wolf Grey
description:
The Nike Kyrie Flytrap V Wolf Grey has become a celebrated addition to the basketball shoe catalog.

The upper section of this Nike Flytrap V is white mesh, with the outline of a stenciled-on silver-gray Swoosh. Criss-crossing containment straps help keep your foot in place, and collar padding is for heel lockdown. The midsole of the forefoot contains a Zoom Air unit designed to compress and spring back into place. The rubber outsole features multidirectional traction that curves up the side of the sneaker in a grey design.

The Nike Kyrie Flytrap V Wolf Grey was release on February 14th, 2022 and retailed for $90.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Wheat Lemon Drop
description: The Travis Scott x Air Max 1 'Wheat' colorway is an exclusive release on the Houston rappers website. Modifying the design of the upper, Scott's take on the AM1 includes a Wheat mesh base with Baroque Brown nubuck overlays. Multicolor webbing straps connect a middle panel to the heel and lace area, while Scott's signature reverse Swoosh is seen on the lateral side profile. Cactus Jack branding can be found on the tongue, as well as a stitched pennant on the back heel. The classic AM1 visible Max Air unit remains intact, painted in to match the color of the midsole, while 'Cactus Corporation' is written on a revised waffle rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Crater Foam Black White

description: A heritage hoops shoes is elevated with a pastel makeover in the SoleFly x Air Jordan 13 Retro 'I’d Rather Be Fishing'. Built on a rubber outsole with panther-paw traction pods in herringbone rubber, subtle branding nods include SoleFly and Jumpman logos alternating on the tongue and the trademark holographic cat eye on the lateral heel. The upper features indented blue suede overlays in powder blue against a background of cream ripstop textile and grey paneling in suede.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 40th Anniversary White Black
Nike SB Dunk Low Pro Be True Xavier Schipani
description: The Nike Dunk Low SB ‘Be True’ honors a classic with a tribute to tolerance. Xavier Schipani, an Austin-based artist identifying as a trans man, created custom graphics to adorn this low-top that celebrates the LGBTQIA+ community. A white mesh base on the upper with leather overlays in vibrant yellow on the forefoot and gradient lilac-to-pink on the heel combine with asymmetrical Swooshes on each side panel in blue and pink. Branding for Nike SB and Be True alternates on the woven tongue tags. The insole salutes the strength and bond of trans communities around the world with a symbolic chain link graphic.

The Yeezy 500 first appeared as a pre-order in February 2018, before a wider release in April 2018. The 'Blush' colorway features a light taupe hue throughout the shoe, including the upper which is comprised of suede, mesh and leather. The sculpted midsole is lifted from the adidas KB8 III, which touted 'Feet You Wear' technology from the 1990s.

Drawing inspiration from an original colorway of the Air Jordan 7, the Air Jordan 3 Retro GS 'Cardinal Red' is a mid-top made for kids. It features a white tumbled leather upper with dark red accents on the eyelets, collar lining, and the raised Jumpman logo on the heel. Additional Jumpman branding is embroidered in orange on the tongue. The 3's signature elephant print is on the eyestay and forefoot and heel overlay. On the bottom is a white and red polyurethane midsole with visible Air-sole cushioning in the heel.

The Air Jordan 9 Retro 'Chile Red' draws inspiration from 2012's 'Motorboat Jones' colorway. Vibrant red features throughout, from the textile utilized on the upper to the speed lacing system. The theme continues through to the tonal patent leather on the mudguard, collar and heel. Black accents arrive on the tongue tag, molded eyelets and pull loop at the heel. A glossy red polyurethane midsole and black rubber outsole complete the iteration. The Jordan 9 'Chile Red' will drop on May 7, 2022.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 Travis Scott Cactus Jack Saturn Gold
description: Travis Scott and Nike team up for an outdoor-inspired shoe in the Nike Air Max 1 'Saturn Gold.' It has a monochrome yellow palette throughout an upper crafted from breathable mesh with stitched leather overlays. It features two-tone rope laces and brown webbing straps that are integrated into the laces and heel overlay with mismatched Cactus Jack and Nike logos on each shoe. A rubber Cactus Jack patch is on the tongue with the rapper's trademark reverse Swoosh on the lateral side. The one-note finish extends to a wedge-shaped foam midsole with Air-sole cushioning in the heel and a waffle-tread rubber outsole underfoot.

Bringing back a two-tone palette initially featured on a low-top release from 1988 and later 2017 is the Air Jordan 13 Retro 'Navy' also known as 'Brave Blue.' The upper combines blue mesh overlays with a black tumbled leather forefoot and matching black synthetic suede throughout the midfoot and heel. An embroidered blue Jumpman is on the tongue, while the 13's holographic cat eye is on the lateral collar. On the bottom is a panther par outsole equipped with herringbone rubber pods. The Jordan 13 'Navy' will drop on April 30, 2022.

Part of a capsule collection that includes footwear and apparel, the iconic cartoon character is front and center in the Hello Kitty x Nike Air Presto ‘University Blue.’ The lifestyle runner’s blue mesh upper is infused with a playful Hello Kitty print while the Air-infused Phylon midsole is patterned with five multicolored dots which refer to the Nike Alpha Project. Additional Hello Kitty appearances on the shoe include her image on the white TPU heel cage and her trademark red bow on the tongue.

The Dunk Low 'University Blue' brings a two-tone look to its retro basketball construction. The shoe's upper features an all-leather build, finished with a white base that's highlighted by University Blue on the overlays and Swoosh branding. A nylon tongue supports the fit, marked by a traditional woven tongue tag, as does a padded collar. Both colors come together on the rubber cupsole that anchors the build.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Rattan Black

colorway: Moon Fossil/Light Orewood Brown-Light Iron Ore-Summit White

shoeName: Nike Air Max Plus atmos White Hyper Jade
description: An old-school runner is presented in a standout colorway with the Nike Air Max Plus ‘White Hyper Jade,’ available only through atmos Tokyo. White mesh pairs with undulating TPU overlays in black and aqua hues. The PU midsole features a midfoot-supporting foot shank that arrives in the shape of a whale tail while aqua-colored Air-sole units deliver cushioning at the heel and forefoot.

The Nike Air Max 97 stands out as an exemplar of the brand's innovation with its water ripple-inspired design. This 'Triple Black' edition matches the heritage of the AM97 as a lifestyle offering, garbed in premium leather and mesh materials. 3M Scotchlite strips supply reflective flair to the monochromatic upper. A multi-window Air midsole and scuff-resistant traction nod to the signature model.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Reverse Panda
description: The heritage court sneaker gets a color reinterpretation of the distinctive ‘Panda’ Dunk colorway. The Nike Dunk Low ‘Reverse Panda’ delivers a tumbled leather upper atop a black foundation with contrasting white overlays and a matching Swoosh, the inverse of the 'Panda' colorway. Black sidewalls with a contrasting white rubber outsole are layered on a traditional cupsole. Traditional Nike branding appears on the tongue tag and back tab.

The UGG Neumel Boot Black features a black suede upper, a single velcro strap over the forefoot and heel, a matching embossed logo on the rear pull tab, and moc-stitch detailing along the shaft.

The upper is fashioned from high-quality leather and features cinch tie laces that can be adjusted down. The UGG Neumel Boot is made with a premium upcycled black wool upper, featuring a rib knit cuff and heel for durability. It also has a lyocell lining to provide cushioned comfort.

The UGG Neumel Boot Black was launched on November 16th, 2021, at a retail price of $130.

The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Flax' emerges with a neutral colorway. Built with Primeknit, the upper appears in Flax, with a post-dyed monofilament stripe revealing interior elements of the shoe. Underfoot, the semitranslucent rubber cage overlays a Boost midsole, giving way to a gum rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 40th Anniversary Sail Malachite
UGG Classic Ultra Mini Brown Driftwood (W)
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Brown Driftwood W was added to the women´s (W) catalog, coming in the black driftwood and brown driftwood colorway.

The primary material used in the making of this shoe is grade-A Twinface sheepskin. The upper has a fine-grained texture while the wool side has a plush finish throughout. The sole boasts a starburst pattern for traction, and the insoles are made of leather linings and natural wool lining. This model has a heel tab and a round toe.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Brown Driftwood W was first released on October 11th, 2022, with $140 being its retail price at that time.

shoeName: Jordan 5 Retro DJ Khaled We The Best Crimson Bliss (GS)
description: A heritage silhouette is treated to a vivid color palette with the DJ Khaled x Air Jordan 5 Retro GS ‘Crimson Bliss,’ a pair from the 2022 ‘We The Best’ collection. Made for little kids, the upper in a brilliant pink features netting at the quarter panel and a luxe interior lining in quilted blue. Built on a foam midsole in off-white with distinctive shark-tooth patterning, Air-sole cushioning and a clear rubber outsole provide comfort and traction underfoot. The tongue in reflective silver is embellished with Jumpman branding and Nike Air and ‘We the Best’ alternate on the overlay on the heel.

shoeName: Nike Sportswear Kids' Tech Fleece Full-Zip Hoodie Dark Grey Heather/Black
silhoutte: Nike Sportswear Kids' Tech Fleece Full-Zip
make: Nike Sportswear Kids' Tech Fleece Full-Zip

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Mellow
description: A kaleidoscopic array of textures and patterns distinguishes the Concepts x Nike Air Max 1 SP ‘Mellow.’ Atop an off-white PU midsole with a faux mud-splatter pattern, the upper in a blue denim tie-dye features a forefoot overlay in cowhide. Burgundy corduroy lines the sneaker and retro bandana prints embellish the heel and collar. The mudguard is dressed in a green military-inspired textile while alternating Swooshes appear in floral and stripes. Rounding out the frenetic combination is a velvet tongue in red with paired branding for Nike and Concepts.

Seattle’s former hoops franchise gets a cameo with the Air Jordan 1 Mid ‘Sonics.’ The retro mid-top features a base on the upper in white intersected by overlays in Noble Green and a color-matched Swoosh. The padded collar and woven tongue tag with Jumpman branding appear in Pollen. A traditional rubber cupsole delivers support underfoot and contains a PU-encased Air-sole unit in the heel for cushioned comfort.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Philadelphia Phillies
description: The Nike Dunk Low Premium SB 'Philadelphia Phillies' is inspired by vintage jerseys of the historic MLB team. The nubuck and suede upper features a light shade of Valor Blue, with a Team Maroon Swoosh outlined with white trim. A contrasting white midsole gives way to a gum rubber outsole where a small patch of pink on the right shoe signifies stepping in bubble gum. Nike SB tags on the outside of the tongue are matched with Philadephia inspired graphics on the inside tongue tags including a cheesesteak on the left shoe and a Liberty Bell on the right.

The Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Jade Horizon' floods Tinker Hatfield's classic 1990 design in a pastel colorway. A pale green shade coats the suede upper, with translucent quarter panel netting on the lateral side and tonal TPU eyelets. A pink Jumpman logo stands out against the silver reflective tongue. The same shade of pink arrives on the signature shark-tooth detailing that appears on the black polyurethane midsole. Air-sole cushioning is visible in the heel, with an icy translucent outsole underfoot.

shoeName: Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex Light Bone
description: The Air Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex 'Light Bone' gives a new take of the legendary sneaker form, updated in Sail and Light Bone. Its upper spotlights a leather base with overlays and the standard Jordan Wings’ Logo. On the upper, a Swoosh emphasizes the design with a nylon tongue. The midsole is built on top of a rubber outsole with a circular build for traction.

Adding a spring-ready two-tone palette with color blocking similar to the original 2001 release is the women's Air Jordan 11 Retro Low 'Pure Violet.' Rope laces go through webbing eyelets to secure a white ballistic mesh upper with a glossy patent leather overlay in a pastel lavender hue. The white Phylon midsole features full-length Nike Air cushioning and is supported by a carbon fiber spring plate and a translucent rubber outsole.

shoeName: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Ice
description: The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Mono Ice' released as part of the four-shoe Mono Pack. Like the other models in the collection, the shoe updates its construction via monofilament mesh, replacing the traditional Primeknit. Finished in light blue throughout, a subtle side stripe cuts through the side wall, while a visible internal cage bolsters the fit. A webbing heel pull-loop is included for easy on and off, and underfoot, the signature rubber cage overlays the full-length Boost midsole. The shoe was an exclusive release in North America, Latin America and China.

The Yeezy Boost 350 ‘Turtle Dove’ was the second shoe released in the adidas Yeezy collection after the Yeezy Boost 750 ‘OG.’ First seen on Kanye and his models at the Yeezy Season 1 fashion show in February 2015, this colorway was anointed 2015’s Shoe of the Year at the Footwear News 29th Annual Achievement Awards. The Yeezy 350 'Turtle Dove' will restock in April 2022.

Originally released in 2009 as part of the two-shoe Raging Bulls pack, the Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Raging Bull' 2021 brings back one of those colorways with this April 2021 release. The shoe's suede upper appears entirely in Varsity Red, contrasted by black eyelets and highlighted by a reflective silver tongue. Mesh inserts maintain the classic Jordan aesthetic, with a toggle lacing system securing the fit. Underfoot, the polyurethane midsole includes visible Air in the heel for cushioning, highlighted by the white and red shark-tooth detailing on the forefoot.

shoeName: Nike Air Humara LX Jacquemus Light Bone Gold (W)
description: Part of a collaboration intended to bring a sports vibe to an everyday silhouette is the Jacquemus x Nike Air Humara LX ‘Sail.’ The leather upper in cream features fuzzy suede overlays in off-white with brown-and-cream ribbon-like webbing eyelets. Adding to the subtly luxe finish is a metallic gold mini-Swoosh adorning the quarter panel. The heel tab and tongue receive Jacquemus branding. Traction and grip are afforded by the chunky rubber outsole with a lug pattern.

Reviving an untraditional colorway that was initially released in 2006 is the 2022 edition of the Air Jordan 7 Retro 'Citrus.' Similiar to the original, the upper is made from black nubuck with a Huarache-like inner sleeve and contrast orange stitching throughout. The Citrus hue is repeated on the angular '23' heel patch and the Jumpman logo embroidered on the lateral collar with a reb webbing pull tab at the heel for easy in and out. Orange and crimson reappear on the black foam midsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning.

Released to celebrate 30 years of the silhouette, the Air Jordan 6 Retro OG 'Carmine' 2021 emerges with a contrasting look. The shoe's upper features a mix of leather and nubuck, finished in white and carmine, with black contrast completing the team look. Underfoot, the midsole houses visible Air in the heel to provide cushioning.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (GS)

description: Inspired by MJ's 'Black Cat' nickname, the Air Jordan 13 features design language lifted from a panther. The 'French Blue' colorway features white tumbled leather on the upper, combined with grey leather on the toe and French Blue suede around the ankle and midsole area. A hologram button on the lateral ankle represents a panther eye, while the outsole reflects a panther paw with segments of herringbone. A pop of red on the Jumpman logo adds a lone color contrast.

shoeName: New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Light Arctic Grey Purple
Jordan 1 Retro High Black Metallic Gold (2020)
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Black Metallic Gold' brings an elevated construction to go with its elevated colorway. The shoe's upper is built with patent leather, finished in black and highlighted by metallic gold on the 'Wings' logo, Swoosh branding, collar and tongue tag. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while underfoot, more metallic gold marks the stitching around the Air midsole.

shoeName: Nike Tech Fleece Joggers Dark Grey Heather/Black
description:
Tech Fleece is Nike’s Dark Grey Heather/Black colorway joggers.

This Nike Tech Fleece jogger is a heavy, breathable 100% cotton fabric. It is all heather grey with a small and outstanding black Nike logo on the left thigh. It features a ribbed waistband with a black elasticated drawstring with loose ends. Two side pockets are available on both sides of the joggers. A more oversized side pocket on the left leg is enclosed with a black zipper. The legs are reinforced with ribbed knit cuffs. Not forgetting, there’s a company label with instructions on handling the jogger on the waist at the back.

This Nike Tech Fleece Joggers was released on 14th Jan 2022, retailing at $110.

shoeName: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Grey
description: Featuring a neutral look, the Comme des Garçons PLAY x Chuck 70 High 'Steel Gray' released as part of a collaboration with the Japanese brand. The shoe's upper is built with canvas, finished in grey and complemented by the heart and eyes logo on the lateral side. Contrast stitching emerges throughout, while chrome eyelets secure the lacing system. Underfoot, co-branding marks the OrthoLite sockliner, which provides cushioning, while a rubber midsole gives way to a brown rubber outsole with a diamond pattern for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 97 Black White Anthricite

description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Chicago Black Toe' updates an iconic look. Drawing from the 'Chicago' colorway, the shoe's familiar mix of black, Gym Red and white includes black on the perforated toe box. Underfoot, the midsole houses Air in the heel for cushioning, with a concentric outsole providing traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low 40th Anniversary Edition Bronx Origins
adidas Sleek Super Beyonce Ivy Park White Blue
description: The Ivy Park x Wmns Super Super Sleek 'White Royal Blue' released as part of a larger collection. Made with the help of Beyoncé's athleisure brand, the shoe's bold construction incorporates a white textile base on the upper, overlaid by tonal leather and highlighted by the Three-Stripes, which appear in blue. The black foxing adds Ivy Park branding, while underfoot, a semitranslucent lugged platform midsole anchors the fit.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Royal Toe
Nike Air Max 90 Leather Triple Black (2020)
Nike Dunk Low LX Pink Foam (W)
Nike Dunk Low Union Passport Pack Argon
description: Drawing from the three-pice 'Passport Pack' which takes inspiration from the early '90s days of the Union crew is the Union LA x Nike Dunk Low 'Argon.' Each style from the pack pays homage to the cities the retailer called or calls home, New York, Los Angeles, and Tokyo. It features unfinished red stitching and a tearaway ripstop upper that reveals a leather underlay in varying shades of blue. On the lateral side is a yellow 'UN/LA' tag with a heel emblem marked with Union's Frontman graphic, which reappears on the blue translucent rubber outsole.

Emerging with a look similar to the 'Iowa' Dunk from 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Pollen' sports familiar color-blocking. Built with leather, the shoe's upper appears with a black base, overlaid by contrasting Pollen, including on the Swoosh branding. A nylon tongue supports the fit, as doe perforations on the toe box. Underfoot, a white Air midsole offers cushioning, giving way to a concentric rubber outsole for traction.

The Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Pine Green' combines updated materials with OG color blocking. The upper's traditional leather construction is replaced with textured nubuck. Pops of green appear on the perforated leather collar, molded eyelets and embroidered Jumpman branding on the tongue. The 3's classic elephant print arrives on the forefoot and heel overlays, with a second Jumpman icon displayed on the molded heel tab. The theme continues underfoot in the form of a white polyurethane midsole with contrast green accents and a grey rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Wolf Grey Pure Platinum
description: The Nike Dunk Low 'Wolf Grey Pure Platinum' is a departure from the classic Dunk look. The upper blends platinum leather with Wolf Grey nubuck overlays, with the Swoosh hiding a contrasting blue outline behind white leather. The traditional woven Nike tongue tag is replaced with a leather patch, affixed with contrasting blue stitches on each corner. Traditional laces are replaced with rope laces, while a blue leather insole completes the updated look.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Snakeskin Washed Teal Bleached Coral
Nike Blazer Low Sacai Black Patent Leather

description: The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Israfil' emerges with a patchwork design on its Primeknit construction. Butil with a mix of tan and grey yarns, the upper is highlighted by the signature monofilament stripe through the construction. Underfoot, a full-length Boost midsole provides cushioning, wrapped in a semitranslucent rubber shell that leads into a gum rubber outsole underfoot.

shoeName: Crocs Pollex Clog by Salehe Bembury Cobbler
description: Renowned footwear designer Salehe Bembury reworks the classic clog with dramatic 'fingerprint' concave ridges and injects it with a vibrant peach hue. The Salehe Bembury x Crocs Pollex Clog ‘Cobbler' features a build of molded foam with distinctive ridges that mirror three of Bembury's fingerprints side by side. Branding for Crocs and Salehe Bembury adorns the orange adjustible heel strap, which helps ensure a secure fit; translucent rubber pods on the outsole offer grippy traction.

shoeName: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Jumbo White Black

description: The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Black Non-Reflective' emerges with an almost-monochromatic look on its signature construction. The shoe's upper is built with Primeknit, finished in black and complemented by a tonal monofilament stripe through the design. A touch of red brings color to the heel loop, while underfoot, a Boost midsole provides cushioning. The TPU shell that overlays the midsole continues down onto the rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike LD Waffle SF sacai Fragment Grey
description: Nike teamed up with Chitose Abe and Hiroshi Fujiwara to create the Fragment Design x sacai x LDV Waffle 'Light Smoke Grey.' Drawing from both the LDV and the Waffle Racer, the shoe's upper is built with a mesh base, overlaid by stacked suede on the forefoot, eyestay and heel. White leather marks the Swooshes, with further doubled-up touches on the laces and tongue. Co-branding emerges on the elongated foam midsole that provides cushioning underfoot, giving way to a contrasting black waffle rubber outsole that's included for traction.

Featuring a subdued look, the Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Taupe Haze' released in January 2021. The shoe's upper is built with a mix of textured suede and cracked leather, finished in Taupe Haze and contrasted by the laces, wings and heel overlay. Infrared 23 highlights the tongue branding and inside of the tongue, while underfoot, a two-tone midsole houses visible Air in the heel for cushioning, with encapsulated Air in the forefoot. A rubber outsole is included for traction. The usual mesh inserts at the quarter panel and vamp complete the classic look.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low NH Cacao Wow
Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2 White Black
description: The React Phantom Run Flyknit 2 'Oreo' gets its name from its classic mix of colors. The shoe's Flyknit upper appears in white, contrasted by black on the supportive Flywire cables. An external heel counter is included for stability, while tongue and heel pull-loops are included for easy on and off. Underfoot, a React midsole provides cushioning.

shoeName: New Balance 550 Sea Salt Macadamia Nut (W)
description: An iconic hoops shoe first introduced in 1989 gets an update with the New Balance Women's 550 ‘Sea Salt Macadamia Nut.’ The off-white suede upper and low-cut collar are made of comfortable padded mesh intersected by a prominent white leather "N" logo on the quarter panel. Classic cupsole tooling and a cream-colored rubber outsole with exposed EVA wedge on the medial side provide comfort and support underfoot.

shoeName: Nike Zoom Cortez SP sacai Iron Grey
description: An iconic silhouette from 1972 receives an artful reinvention with the sacai x Nike Zoom Cortez SP ‘Iron Grey.’ This version of the Cortez appears in greyscape layers of nylon and suede and features two layered collars, tongues and signature Swooshes. The familiar wedge of the original accompanies a reconstructed foam midsole with an exposed Zoom Air unit in the forefoot. The herringbone-patterned rubber outsole provides all-day comfort and traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Mid QS Chocolate
description: A retro silhouette gets a luxe build with the Nike Air Force 1 Mid ‘Chocolate.’ A decadent velvet suede in chocolate on the upper is intersected by a signature Swoosh, collar lining and laces in cream. The latter are delivered in variable widths and combine with the adjustable ankle strap for a comfortable locked-down fit. The midsole appears in pale tan and features an interior Air-sole unit in the heel and a pivot-point traction pattern on the rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Black White Pebbled Leather

colorway: Green Apple/Reflect Silver/University Red/Bright Crimson/Blue Chill
description:
The Nike LeBron 20 Christmas, with a colorway reminiscent of the Grinch character, is the 20th signature shoe of the NBA´s champion.

The woven upper in green apple has a university red threaded throughout. A bright crimson Swoosh is superimposed over a reflective silver Swoosh on the lateral side with a smaller crimson Swoosh on the medial. The holly patterning visible beneath the translucent blue chill outsole is also found on the red Swooshes and the green tongue and heel tab. The lightweight cushion midsole has an Air Zoom Turbo Unit on the forefoot and an Air Zoom Unit on the heel.

The Nike LeBron 20 Christmas debuted on December 25th, 2022, for $200 retail.

shoeName: Nike Air Terra Forma Off-White Wheat Green Strike
description: The Off-White x Nike Air Terra Forma ‘Wheat’ takes a heritage hiking shoe of the late ‘80s and early ‘90s and treats it to a reinvention by a legendary designer. With black rubber outsoles outfitted with oversized spikes, the midsole with an exposed Max Air unit appears in an array of melded orange, blue, pink and pale green. A zippered cover on the neon green tongue reveals a shape evoking the Air Jordan 6, one of the late Virgil Abloh’s favorite models, while a clear stitched Swoosh adorns the upper. The outsole declares ‘Tread Lightly’ in exaggerated block letters.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low Multi-Swoosh Black Orange
Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit Hyper Violet
silhoutte: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit
make: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit

shoeName: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rookie Of The Year
Jordan 1 Mid SE Orange Wear Away
New Balance 9060 Ivory Cream Pink Sand
Nike Air Max Plus Black University Blue (2022)
Nike Epic Phantom React Flyknit Icon Clash Gunsmoke (W)
silhoutte: Nike Epic Phantom React Flyknit Icon Clash
make: Nike Epic Phantom React Flyknit Icon Clash

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Black Croc
Nike Air Force 1 Low React Black White
Nike Air Dunk Jumbo Mint Foam
Nike Zoom Vomero 5 Wheat Grass Cacao Wow
Nike Dunk Low Valentine's Day Yellow Heart (W)
description: Celebrate love in style with the Nike Women's Dunk Low 'Valentine's Day.' The sleek and simple design features a white base in tumbled leather and tonal leather overlays for a refined look. The white rubber cupsole keeps the shoes clean and classic. Bright yellow accents add a pop of color to the woven Nike tongue tags, stitched back tab and heart graphic on the heel.

Recrafting the build of the original 1988 design by Tinker Hatfield is the Air Jordan 3 Retro SE 'Muslin.' The upper is constructed from Muslin canvas with the forefoot and heel overlays in Cement Grey suede. University Red accents land on the sneaker's lower eyelets, as well as Jumpman branding on the tongue and molded heel panel. It's built on an off-white polyurethane midsole with visible Air-sole cushioning in the heel and a durable grey rubber outsole.

Originally released in 2013, the Air Jordan 5 Retro brings back the two-tone look with this 2021 release. Faithful to the original, the shoe's upper is built with suede, finished in black and contrasted by white on the collar lining, interior tongue and heel branding. Translucent netting marks the quarter panel, while tonal TPU eyelets bolster the lacing system. Underfoot, a white polyurethane midsole includes visible Air in the heel to provide cushioning, with speckled shark-tooth detailing accenting the forefoot. An icy translucent rubber outsole offers traction and deviates from the black-and-white design.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid Mystic Navy Mint Foam
Jordan 1 Retro High OG Patent Bred (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Patent Bred' is a shoe made for older kids that delivers a glossy spin on the iconic OG colorway from 1985. Entirely made with patent leather, the upper features a black base with contrasting crimson accents on the toe box, Swoosh, and collar and heel overlays. Traditional branding elements are featured in the form of a woven Nike tongue tag and Wings logo that's stamped on the lateral ankle. The high-top is built on a sturdy rubber cupsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning in the heel.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Phantom Gold Suede (W)

description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High '85 'Georgetown' pays tribute to the shoe's OG silhouette with a restored heritage build. The two-tone design commemorates the 40th anniversary of Michael Jordan's title-clinching shot against the Hoyas on March 29, 1982, pairing a light grey base with contrasting College Navy overlays. Signature details include a woven Nike Air tag on the nylon tongue and a retro Wings logo stamped on the lateral ankle. The classic high-top is mounted on a rubber cupsole, with an Air-sole heel unit encapsulated in polyurethane.

shoeName: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Iridescent Dreams

description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Royal Toe' updates a classic colorway. Built with leather, the upper appears in white with black overlays, highlighted by hits of Game Royal on the collar and toe box. A lightly padded nylon tongue supports the fit, while underfoot, a white Air midsole gives way to more Game Royal on the circular outsole.

Part of the first 350 release in 2019, the Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Hyperspace' features a neutral colorway. The shoe's flexible Primeknit upper appears in Hyperspace, with a microfilament vent running through design. A heel loop and rope laces support the fit, while underfoot, the translucent midsole reveals a full-length Boost midsole. The shoe released exclusively in select cities in Africa, the Middle East, India and Asia Pacific.

shoeName: Nike LD Waffle SF sacai Fragment Blue Void
description: Bringing together two renowned Japanese labels, the Fragment Design x sacai x LDV Waffle 'Blackened Blue' is a collaborative look. Combining features of the Nike LDV and Waffle Racer, the shoe's hybrid construction emerges in mesh and suede, finished in navy and contrasted by white throughout, including on the dual leather Swooshes. The heel patch adds Nike and sacai branding, while the double tongues sport Nike and fragment branding. Underfoot, more co-branding marks the elongated foam midsole, with a waffle rubber outsole included for traction.

shoeName: Nike LD Waffle sacai CLOT Kiss of Death 2 Cool Grey
description: Inspired by CLOT's Air Max 1 release from 2013 comes the triple-threat collaboration shoe that is the sacai x CLOT x Nike LDWaffle 'Kiss Of Death 2.' The sneaker showcases neutral grey tones throughout an upper crafted from semi-translucent mesh with fused synthetic overlays. Nike x sacai x CLOT branding is featured on the leather heel tab with woven Nike tags on the grey and green nylon tongues. It is built on a double-stacked foam midsole that's reinforced underfoot by a waffle-traction gum rubber outsole.

shoeName: Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey
description: Released in May 2021, the Air Jordan 13 Retro 'Red Flint' features a look inspired by the 1998 'Flint' colorway. The shoe's upper is defined by the Gym Red accents on the inside of the tongue, collar lining and reflective mesh overlays, replacing the blue of the OG look. The upper itself is built with a white leather base, overlaid by Flint Grey synthetic suede and sporting the usual hologram logo on the ankle. Underfoot, a panther's-paw outsole provides traction.

shoeName: Air Jordan 1 Low Vintage Stealth Grey
adidas Yeezy 350 V2 CMPCT Slate Bone
Jordan 5 Retro DJ Khaled We The Best Sail
description: The DJ Khaled x Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Sail' uses pastel hues and subtle logo highlights for its part in the ‘We the Best’ capsule collection. An off-white leather upper is highlighted by pastel embellishments and a powder-blue quilted lining, contrasting with the Air-assisted polyurethane midsole in Violet Star. The tongue features the classic Jumpman logo against a reflective silver finish, with 'Keep Going' hidden on its interior side. The two heel overlays contrast, with one adorned by the Nike Air log while the other proclaiming 'We the Best,' which also decorates the right shoe's translucent rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Air Max Terrascape Plus Black Lime
description: Applying a simple two-tone palette to a lifestyle runner taken from the 1998 original Air Max Plus is the Nike Air Max Terrascape Plus 'Black Barely Volt.' It features sustainable materials such as an Air-assisted Crater Foam midsole and a rubber outsole made with Nike Grind. Unique branding elements include an oversized Barely Volt Swoosh and a 'TS' heel badge inspired by the original Tuned Air logo. The black textile upper is made from recycled polyester and overlaid with a semi-translucent TPU cage integrated into the laces for security.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Burnt Olive W is a slip-on footwear for women that can be worn as either a slipper or a shoe.

This Burnt Tasman Slipper model has an upper section made from soft suede with embroidered braiding around the cuff. The plush lining combines sheepskin and upcycled wool and the insole is made from upcycled wool. The outsole is made of Treadlite by UGG and features a starburst traction pattern. This sustainable slipper with a heat embossed logo is held together by 100% recycled polyester fiber binding.

The UGG Tasman Slipper Burnt Olive W was released on November 1st, 2021 at a retail price of $100.

The UGG Tazz Slipper Black W takes on the slip-in silhouette, and retains most of the classics of the shoe brand, including the suede upper, wool lining, and the Treadlite rubber outsole.

The Tazz Slipper Black for women has a black suede upper, with a patterned multicolor collar providing the only contrast. On the inside, it features plush UGG sheepskin wool throughout the lining. The foam footbed is present in the rest of the underfoot. UGG maintains its signature Treadlite rubber outsole for traction under a 1.5-inch platform sole.

The UGG Tazz Slipper Black W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021 for an initial retail price of $120.

Looking to one of Michael Jordan's oldest nicknames, the Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Black Cat' 2020 brings back a 2006 colorway. Built with suede, the upper appears entirely in black, save for a hit of Light Graphite on the tongue branding. Underfoot, the Air midsole continues the tonal look, giving way to a rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Fleece Swoosh Worn Blue
UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Black (W)
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Black W is an addition to the women's collection by UGG, available in a black pattern.

This shoe features an asymmetrical topline upper constructed with sheepskin and soft suede. 17mm UGGplush, which comprises 80% wool and 20% lyocell, is used on the interior lining. Other details include a heel pull tab, overlock stitch detailing on the exterior, and a leather heel label with the UGG logo. A 3.5" shaft height and 2 inches platform supported by an EVA midsole and Treadlite outsole complete the design. 

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Black W was released on October 10th, 2022. Initially, it retailed at $150.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 PRM Duck Honey Dew
description: The Nike Air Max 1 Premium ‘Honeydew’ pairs a rich mix of materials with a standout colorway on a heritage favorite. The upper features suede overlays in dark grey with a light green Swoosh layered on a backdrop of black suede. Additional hits of color appear on the eyelets, mudguard and the lining of the collar in orange. Standard Nike Air branding on the heel overlay is replaced by a stitched duck graphic. Comfort and grip are afforded by the PU midsole in white with an exposed Air-sole unit atop a rubber outsole in light green.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP Travis Scott Black Phantom (TD)
Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage Mismatched Swoosh Blue Red
Nike PG 6 Black Peach Cream Celestine Blue
Louis Vuitton LV Trainer White Black White
UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Driftwood (W)
description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Driftwood W has become a popular addition to the women´s (W) catalog.

This Classic Ultra Mini model in a driftwood color scheme has a shaft height of 3.5 inches (89 mm) and a platform height of 2 inches (51 mm). The upper section is made of suede with an asymmetrical top line, a heel pull tab, and seams with overlock stitching. The lining and insole are made of UGGplush, the midsole of EVA, and the outsole of Treadlite by UGG.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Platform Driftwood W debuted on October 11, 2022 for $150 retail.

shoeName: Nike Dunk High Retro BTTYS TCU
adidas Samba OG Collegiate Green Gum
adidas Gazelle Bold Pulse Mint Pink (W)
Nike SB Dunk Low Los Angeles Dodgers
colorway: Deep Royal Blue/White-Sport Red-Gum Light Brown
description: Inspired by the Los Angeles Dodgers MLB team, this NIke Dunk Low SB features colors and details from the storied franchise. The upper is constructed with a white leather base, with blue suede overlays and a blue textile Swoosh. The inside tongue tags feature a palm tree graphic on the left shoe and Dodger Stadium's welcome sign on the right shoe. A white midsole leads to a gum rubber outsole, with a small splotch of pink on the right shoe, depicting the look of bubblegum stuck on the heel.

Built for younger kids is the 2021 edition of the Air Jordan 11 Retro GS 'Cool Grey' brings back a classic colorway for its' 20th anniversary. Similar to the original design, the mid-top features a grey nubuck upper with a tonal patent leather mudguard. A stylized '23' is featured on the textile heel tab, while a white Jumpman logo is embroidered on the lateral ankle. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a white Phylon midsole, enhanced with an encapsulated Air-sole unit and reinforced by a translucent rubber outsole.

The 'Black Panda' colorway of the Nike Dunk Low is simple and clean, featuring an all-leather build across the upper. Black smooth leather dominates the paneled upper, while white supplies a pop of color on the laces, Swoosh and midsole. Blacked out tongue tags and back heel stitching matches the overall color concept of the shoe, while the traditional Dunk herringbone outsole finishes the look.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Sun Club Arctic Orange
description: A heritage favorite gets a beach-ready reinvention with playful branding in the Nike Dunk Low ‘Sun Club.’ The upper features a color-blocked mix of materials made in part with recycled content. Overlays in tumbled leather appear in Sanded gold against a base in blue, pink and lime green textile. Alternating blue and yellow Swooshes accompany tongue tags embellished with ‘Nike Sun Club,’ while palm trees and a smiling sun are stitched at the heel.

Pale pink and elephant print distinguish this otherwise low-key women's mid-top. The women’s Air Jordan 3 Retro ‘Neapolitan’ delivers an allover white upper in tumbled leather with a subtle powder pink constrasting with Dark Mocha brown in the signature elephant-print overlays; pink is repeated in the heel at the midsole. The tongue and back heel feature Jumpman branding in shades of matching brown and pink. The classic midsole in off-white PU ensures cushion with its visible Air-sole unit and rides on a brown rubber outsole.

The women’s Air Jordan 1 Low ‘University Blue’ utilizes a colorway at the heart of MJ's college days. The upper in a light grey leather pairs with University Blue overlays at the forefoot and heel, the signature Swoosh and the collar. Branding appears on the heel and tongue with sstitched Wings and Jumpman logos. Underfoot, support and comfort are ensured by a traditional rubber cupsole with an internal Air-sole unit housed in a cushy foam wedge.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Stussy Fossil
description: A monochrome finish pairs with hemp canvas in the Stussy x Nike Air Force 1 Mid ‘Fossil.’ The mid-top brings off-white hemp to the usually leather upper and is intersected by an intricately stitched signature Swoosh. The tongue tag and ankle strap, adjustable for a secure fit, display Stussy branding that is echoed with its double-S logo on the toe box and on the pony-hair heel tab’s metal badge. Underfoot, cushion and comfort are ensured by the rubber cupsole in cream with an interior Air-sole unit.

The Nike Air Force 1 Mid White '07 features a smooth white leather upper with matching overlays and Swooshes. From there, a velcro strap with Nike Swoosh embroidery and a matching Air sole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 Mid White '07 was re-released in December of 2015 and retailed for $95.

A heritage basketball silhouette is rendered in a memorable color palette with the Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Teal Zeal.’ The white base establishes a neutral base for the upper with contrasting overlays in Washed Teal with a matching Swoosh. The rubber outsole and tongue tag with Nike branding add additional hues in Kumquat. The shoe is outfitted for all-day wear with a cushy low-cut collar and plush tongue, while grip is ensured by circle-patterned traction underfoot.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SP Undefeated 5 On It Black
description: In the third installment of the 'Dunk vs AF-1' series by Undefeated, this Nike Dunk Low has a vibrant mix of materials in the upper. With perforated suede on the toe and a suede paneling along the forefoot and heel, the signature Swoosh is made of pony hair and the collar and tongue of mesh and nylon. The classic Five Strikes logo from Undefeated is on the woven tongue tag and lateral heel. You'll be walking on a black midsole and a translucent rubber outsole.

The 2018 version of the Air Jordan 11 Retro ‘Concord’ shows off ‘45’ imprinted on the black heel tab in honor of the jersey number that Michael Jordan wore when he returned to the NBA after his first retirement. The shoe’s other signature details remain intact, including a white ballistic mesh upper, black patent leather overlays, and an icy translucent outsole.

shoeName: adidas NMD R1 Primeblue Triple Black
Nike Air Max 90 Recraft Wolf Grey

description:
The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Black W comes in an all-black color scheme. The upper of this shoe is made from soft twin-face sheepskin.

The upper of this Mini Black model for women (W) comes with 17mm sheepskin lining throughout. The UGGplush™ technology was used in crafting the insoles of this shoe. The back of this UGG Classic shoe features a black colored "UGG" printing and its textile binding is made from recycled polyester fibers.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Black W was released in the market on 23rd May 2022 and its retail price was $140.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid Craft Inside Out Black
Nike Air Force 1 Low Drake NOCTA Certified Lover Boy (Includes Love You Forever Special Edition Book)
description: Drake-inspired details imbue the NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Certified Lover Boy’, an understated version of the unmistakable white-on-white AF1 colorway. Asymetric NOCTA and Nike Air branding on each heel tab ornament the white tumbled leather upper, with a nod to heritage details with a perforated toe box, variable width lacing and a low-cut padded collar. Drake's final wink is ‘Love You Forever’ inscribed in embossed lettering across the lateral sidewall of its white midsole, giving this classic a 2022 twist

The New Balance 990v3 Grey 2019 is one of the 2019 releases by shoe manufacturer New Balance.

The New Balance 990v3 Grey 2019 comes in grey and features a leather upper section. The upper part is also made of mesh patches in grey. In addition, the shoe has an ENCAP midsole cushioning with a lightweight foam combined with a rim made of durable polyurethane. The shoe also has white laces for a secure fit and the New Balance logo on both sides.

The New Balance 990v3 Grey 2019 was released on 1st October 2019 to retail at $165.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 High '07 SP Billie Eilish Sequoia
description: The iconic Air Force 1 gets a modern reinvention with the Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 High ‘07 SP ‘Sequoia.’ In a bulky design with five closure straps affixed with modern hardware, the upper in synthetic nubuck is delivered in an earthy dark green. Underfoot, the shoe is true to its heritage roots with Air cushioning delivering lasting comfort on a rubber cupsole, also in green. The singer's profile logo adorns the lace dubraes, and 'Billie Eilish' is emblazoned on the rear of the footbed.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Chenille Swoosh Sail Grand Purple
description: Evoking the aesthetic of vintage varsity letterman jackets, the Nike Dunk Low ‘Grand Purple’ mixes tried-and-true details in a modern look. The upper in leather arrives in a white base with overlays at the heel and forefoot in purple. Underfoot, a traditional cupsole with sidewalls in white is supported atop a rubber outsole in purple for optimal traction. The signature Swoosh appears in a fuzzy purple chenille outlined by Neptune Green, a hue repeated on the sockliner. Branding is featured on the back tab and tongue.

shoeName: Jordan 4 Retro Travis Scott Cactus Jack
description: The Travis Scott x Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Cactus Jack' honors the rapper’s hometown of Houston. Its palette borrows from the team colors of the city’s former Oilers football team, and features a Durabuck leather upper in University Blue, while its insole and branding are dressed in Varsity Red. Completing the look are a black lace cage and speckled light blue heel panel.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low Billie Eilish Sequoia
description: An iconic sneaker gets an eco-conscious makeover with the Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Sequoia.’ Eilish and Nike branding appear on the sockliners made from recycled foam and the outsole is constructed from Nike Grind. The upper in dark green with tonal stitching features textile left over from an earlier AF1 High collab with the pop star and is delivered in a patchwork array of synthetic suede.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP AMBUSH Game Royal
description: Designer Yoon Ahn brings her unique sensibilities to the AMBUSH x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Game Royal.’ The heritage favorite features a monochrome royal blue upper in textured leather. Vibrant hits of Vivid Sulpher appear via an exaggerated Swoosh, tongue tag, TPU heel clip, heel tab and ‘AF 1’ lace dubraes. Anchoring the shoe underfoot is a royal blue rubber cupsole with Air-sole cushioning.

shoeName: Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Purple Velvet (W)
Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape White Photon Dust

description: The Yeezy Boost 700 V2 'Tephra' brings a subdued colorway to the second iteration of the Yeezy 700 line. The shoe's upper is built with a layered mix of mesh and suede, finished in neutral hues. A darker look emerges on the signature bulky sole unit, which houses a full-length Boost midsole for cushioning. Underfoot, a gum rubber outsole provides traction while offering an elevated finish.

shoeName: Reebok Pump Omni Zone II Chalk Vector Blue
Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Midnight Navy

description: Marking the diamond anniversary of the NBA, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE GS ‘Diamond’ presents a low-key colorway on a hoops mid-top. The upper in white leather features contrasting black suede on the signature Swoosh, forefoot overlay and mid-cut collar. The ubiquitous Jumpman appears in a diamond on the tongue tag to symbolize the 75th anniversary of the league’s founding. Comfort and spring on the court are provided by the white midsole with an interior Air-sole unit in the heel atop a translucent rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Two Tone Grey
Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Sail Sea Glass
description: Updating the classic retro runner with a modern build made with at least 20% recycled content by weight is the Nike Air Max Terrascape 90 'Sail.' The upper features off-white ripstop textile with tonal synthetic suede overlays and translucent TPU eyelets. Contrasting black accents are on the signature Swoosh and a webbing pull-loop at the heel. It's built on a Crater Foam midsole, wrapped in a translucent cage and fitted with a Max Air unit in the heel with a waffle-tread rubber outsole made in part with Nike Grind.

Taken from the original 'Iowa' colorway from the 1985 series 'Be True to Your School' is the Nike Dunk Low 'Goldenrod.' Like the original high-top edition, it features a simple two-tone color scheme throughout the leather upper with a solid black base and contrasting yellow overlays. Standard branding elements include a woven Nike tag on the black nylon tongue and a Nike wordmark embroidered on the heel tab. It rides on a durable rubber cupsole that pairs white sidewalls with a yellow rubber outsole.

A golf shoe with Jordan hoops heritage characterizes the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf ‘UNC.’ Delivered in the colors of MJ’s alma mater, the upper in stark white features University Blue overlays. Branding adorns the heel tab with a Wings logo while the ubiquitous Jumpman appears on the tongue tag. Reminiscent of the original Air Jordan 1 is the midsole with its interior Air-sole unit in the heel atop an outsole whose traction pattern provides optimal grip for the greens.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High Hyper Royal Smoke Grey
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Hyper Royal' brings a weathered look to the basketball classic. The shoe's upper features a white leather base, overlaid by suede that sports a faded blue aesthetic. Light Smoke Grey complements the Swoosh and padded collar, while underfoot, a white Air midsole is included for cushioning. Further Light Smoke Grey emerges on the concentric rubber outsole.

Giving the classic silhouette a pastel springtime makeover is the Air Jordan 5 Retro SE 'Easter.' The smooth nubuck upper finished in Regal Pink features traditional AJ5 elements, including TPU eyelets, lace locks, and quarter-panel netting. Embroidered Jumpman branding is on the heel overlay and pale green padded tongue. On the inside, the sockliner displays vibrant bands of color in a nod to the tradition of dyed Easter eggs. On the bottom is an Air-assisted polyurethane midsole with speckled shark-tooth detailing and a green-tinged translucent rubber outsole that glows in the dark.

shoeName: Nike Air Trainer 1 SP Travis Scott Grey Haze
description: Travis Scott works with Nike Sportswear on slight redesign of the classic Air Trainer 1. Replacing the traditional leather build and familiar panels, Scott opts for a textile finish in Grey Haze hue. 'Cactus Corporation' appears on the forefoot strap and back heel area, where a zippered stash pocket can be found. Scott's signature reverse Swoosh is found on the medial side, and Cactus Jack branding appears on the perforated nubuck tongue. Tiny holes can be found all over the upper, which are attachment points for a removable ripstop shroud (that can be stored in the pocket when not in use). Finally, the midsole shape stays the same, but the outsole traction is covered with rows of little nubs, forming a unique grippy pattern.

Jackie Robinson broke baseball's color barrier on April 15, 1947, suiting up for the Brooklyn Dodgers. This Nike Dunk Low celebrates the 75th anniversary of this pivotal sports moment, decking out the retro silhoutte in an off-white base and royal blue overlays. Jackie Robinson details can be found all over the shoe, including printed inspirational quotes on the upper and sockliner, a 75th anniversary tongue tag and his #42 on the lateral heel.

Released in April 2021, the Dunk Low 'Team Green' is a low-top iteration of a 2020 Dunk in Michigan State colors. Built with leather, the shoe's upper appears in a school mix of white and Team Green, with the usual perforations on the toe box offering breathability. A nylon tongue further supports the fit, while underfoot, the rubber cupsole continues the two-tone look, incorporating a concentric traction pattern on the outsole originally designed for basketball.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High Element Gore-Tex Black Particle Grey
description: Updating the iconic silhouette with a new build designed to handle weather is the Air Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex 'Black Particle Grey.' A waterproof Gore-Tex membrane lines the upper, which is constructed from dark green textile with nubuck overlays in black and grey. 3M reflective Swooshes offer more visibility in low-light conditions and a crimson Nike Air logo is on the woven tongue tag with a Gore-Tex wordmark stamped on the later heel. The sneaker is built on an outsole of translucent and opaque black rubber.

A pre-school shoe, the Dunk Low PS 'Triple Pink' also known as 'Barbie' revists the popular basketball silhouette in an interesting new hue. The leather upper offers a new take away the traditional two-tone color blocking with a light pink base and overlays accented by a hot pink Nike Swoosh. A breathable nylon tongue and rubber outsole secure the build of the sneaker.

The Wmns Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Shimmer' is a neutral take on the iconic basketball design. The shoe's upper features a leather construction, finished in a series of tan hues and complemented by the quarter panel netting. Molded eyelets secure the fit, while the tongue includes metallic silver Jumpman branding to highlight the look. Underfoot, the midsole houses the usual visible Air in the heel to provide cushioning, giving way to a herringbone rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 Patta Waves Noise Aqua (with Bracelet)
description: Patta and Nike came together again to bring the Patta x Nike Air Max 1 'Noise Aqua.' The standout feature is a wavy suede mudguard, rendered in a bright blue finish with an embroidered mini-Swoosh on the lateral forefoot. The remaining upper is made from matte silver mesh with white leather overlays and a blue suede Swoosh. The mesh tongue features a woven Patta tag, and an embroidered Nike Air branding rests on the back heel. Lightweight cushioning is featured by a pre-yellowed polyurethane midsole with a visible Air unit under the heel.

shoeName: Nike Air Trainer SC High Auburn
Jordan 1 Retro High OG Light Fusion Red
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Light Fusion Red' brings a vibrant look to its classic basketball construction. Built with leather, shoe's upper features a white base, overlaid by Light Fusion Red and sporting Laser Orange on the Swoosh branding. The tongue tag features a gradient mix of the latter two hues, while underfoot, the white midsole houses Air in the heel for cushioning, giving way to a concentric rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk High Next Nature Toasty Rattan
description: A cozy, eco-conscious build distinguishes the Nike Dunk High Retro Next Nature ‘Rattan,’ one pair in the ‘Toasty’ collection. The white and cream upper is delivered in quilted textile composed of 100% recycled polyester and adorned with a signature Swoosh in black synthetic suede. A fleece lining offers warm comfort for cooler temperatures, while the rubber outsole with pivot-circle patterning provides grippy traction underfoot. Branding appears on the lateral side via black and orange woven tags.

Using refreshed materials and prints to the iconic model is the Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Patchwork.' A dark beige hue is featured on the canvas and textile upper with diverging overlays in moss green and woodland camo. The segmented mudguard has a mix of beige herringbone twill and grey rain camo with an olive green shaggy suede heel overlay. The heel tab has a customization option with a removable hook-and-loop fastener patch. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a two-tone polyurethane midsole with a red-tinged Air-sole unit under the heel.

shoeName: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Clay
description: Featuring a one-note finish emblematic of the larger collection, the Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Mono Clay' released as part of the Mono Pack. Bringing an updated construction to the signature design. Built with monofilament mesh in place of the usual Primeknit, the shoe's upper appears entirely in orange, with slight variation provided by the side stripe. An internal cage is included for support, and a heel pull-loop offers easy on and off. Underfoot, full-length Boost, wrapped in a rubber cage, offers cushioning, while the shoe itself released exclusively in Asia Pacific and China.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High NC to Chi Leather (W)
description: The Wmns Air Jordan 1 High OG 'UNC to Chicago' looks to Michael Jordan's basketball journey to create a hybrid colorway. The shoe's heel starts off in college, with a Dark Powder Blue look modeled after the University of North Carolina Tar Heels. The toe sports Gym Red as a nod to the Chicago Bulls, while the rest of the leather construction is finished in black. Underfoot, a white Air midsole gives way to a Gym Red outsole.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High CO Japan Neutral Grey (2020)
description: Originally released exclusively in Japan and limited to 2,001 pairs, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG CO.JP 'Tokyo' returned in 2020. Built with grey nubuck, the upper is highlighted by hits of metallic silver on the Swoosh and heel overlay. Nike Air branding replaces the Jumpman on the tongue, while the sockliner sports 'CO.JP.' The inside label on the tongue sports both 2001 and 2020, honoring the two releases.

shoeName: Nike Air VaporMax Plus Triple Red
New Balance 550 White Black Rain Cloud

description: The Two 18 x Air Jordan 2 Retro Low SP bring a new look and feel to the AJ2 franchise. Blue-and-red piping contrasts against tan nubuck on the upper with overlays of earthy brown. Also elevating the classic silhouette are refined details including tortoiseshell eyelets and interior lined in leather with Two 18 branding. The tongue is embellished with the Wings logo. The cream midsole offers cushion via an Air-sole unit, and ease of wear and durability are ensured by the rubber outsole.

The Air Jordan 1 Low 'Light Smoke Grey' gives a new iteration of the iconic shoe design, updated in Light Smoke Grey and Gym Red. Its upper spotlights a leather base with overlays and the signature Wings’ Logo. On the upper, a Swoosh branding emphasizes the design with a Nike branded nylon tongue. The midsole is built on top of a rubber outsole with a circular build for traction.

shoeName: Nike Kyrie Low 5 1 World 1 People Orchid
description:
The Nike Kyrie Low 5 1 World 1 People Orchid, made of a meshed upper material, features a range of color combinations and has a floral motif on the heel.

This sneaker is mostly covered in orchid pink, combined with a yellow color theme appearing on the Swoosh logo and on the stitchery displayed on the tongue. The outsole shares a light mint color tone with the forefoot eyelets and the design appearing on the heel. The midsole has magenta pink.

The Nike Kyrie Low 5 1 World 1 People Orchid debuted on July 8th, 2022, and retailed at $110.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi-Patent Pink Prime
description: Celebrating the 40th anniversary of the iconic silhouette, the Undefeated x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Pink Prime’ is one pair from the AF1 Multi-Color Patent project and recalls Undefeated’s Nike Dunk High NL from 2005. The paneled upper in pale blue, black, brown and purple patent leather features hits of contrasting hues with a clear pink Swoosh and yellow tongue tag adorned with the Five Strikes logo, which also appears on the lateral heel. Underfoot, a green rubber cupsole provides support for all-day wear.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low SP Undefeated Multi-Patent Total Orange
description: The Undefeated x Nike Air Force 1 Low ‘Celestine Blue’ gives this heritage favorite a glossy makeover. The upper features panels in jewel shades of green, purple, salmon and aqua, against which a clear blue Swoosh floats. The lace dubraes are embellished with ‘UNDFTD’ while the tongue tage, lateral heel and sockliner include salutes to Undefeated with the Five Strikes logo. Cushion and grip underfoot are delivered via a midsole in off white with Air-sole cushioning atop a gum rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk High 1985 Enamel Green Denim (W)
description: The Nike Women’s Dunk High 1985 ‘Green Denim’ takes a heritage hoops shoe and gives it a distressed makeover. Enamel Green overlays in a stitched weathered finish stand out against the upper in white leather. The sockliner and tongue tag supply subtle Nike branding. A traditional cupsole with off-white sidewalls rides on a green rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike LeBron 3 The Shop Black University Red (2022)
Nike Air Terra Forma Off-White Summit White Psychic Purple
description: The unique sensibilities of the late Virgil Abloh are exhibited in the extravagant details of the Off-White x Nike Air Terra Forma ‘White.’ Delivered on a trail-ready silhouette with aggressively spiked rubber outsoles, the off-white upper features textile with a woodgrain pattern, overlays in suede and a clear stitched Swoosh. A zippered cover partially shields the purple tongue, which evokes the Air Jordan 6 which was among Abloh’s favorite models. Pink, pale green, blue and orange melded accents adorn the midsole and heel counter, and comfort is afforded by the exposed Air-sole unit in the heel. ‘Tread Lightly’ appears on the outsole in oversized block lettering.

shoeName: Nike Air More Uptempo 96 Red Toe

description: UNC's team colors help inform the Air Jordan 13 Retro GS ‘Black University Blue.’ The upper features an array of materials including reflective mesh overlays and tumbled leather in black paired with Carolina blue suede panels. Black Cat inspiration appears via the holographic eye badge on the heel and herringbone-patterned traction in the shape of a panther’s paw underfoot.

The Stussy x Nike Air Penny 2 ’Black’ presents a heritage silhouette in a noir finish. The white Stussy logo appears on the lateral quarter panel of the otherwise all-black upper, which is constructed from hemp canvas and embellished with tonal stitching. The black Phylon midsole features a Zoom Air unit in the forefoot, a Max Air unit in the heel, and a carbon fiber shank which provide optimal support underfoot. The sneaker is easy to put on and take off with pull tabs at the heel and tongue.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Valentine’s Day (2023)
colorway: Light Ivory/Medium Pink/White/Night Brown/Medium Pink/Light Ivory

description: The adidas Yeezy Foam Runner 'Sulfur' slip-on features an all-over pale ochre finish, built from EVA foam and hydroponically produced algae. Ventilation ports providing breathability are visible on the vamp and side panels. A raised sculpted heel offers a supportive, comfortable fit. A wave-patterned outsole anchors the lightweight design and adds traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 SP Concepts Heavy
description: Inspired by the culture and tastes of the late 60’s, the Concepts x Nike Air Max 1 SP 'Heavy' combines an array of textures, colors and patterns. Blue tie-dye denim forms the base of the upper and is overlaid with cowhide at the forefoot, alluding to the dairy farm where the legendary Woodstock festival took place. A brown corduroy lining in the interior, camouflage tiger print on the mudguard, and several versions of bandana print dress the collar and heel overlay. The signature Swoosh alternates from florals to stripes on either side, and additional branding for Concepts and Nike is shared on the tongue tags. Evoking the muddy grounds of an outdoor music festival is the mud splatter pattern adorning the midsole.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Dark Marina Blue (GS)
description: The high-top Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS 'Dark Marina Blue,' is a kid shoe that dresses the classic silhouette in a simple two-tone color scheme. Its' leather upper combines a stealthy black base with contrasting blue overlays at the forefoot and heel. A Nike tag is woven on the breathable nylon tongue, while a retro Wings logo is on the lateral collar flap. On the bottom, is a standard rubber cupsole with an Air-sole heel unit in a lightweight foam wedge.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Bleached Coral (GS)
description: A big kids’ high-top is delivered in a muted colorway with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG GS ‘Stage Haze.’ Overlays at the forefoot in cracked black leather and grey suede at the heel pair with an all-white base intersected by the signature Swoosh in black. The tongue tag with ‘Nike Air’ adds a hit of Bleached Coral and additional branding appears on the lateral ankle with a classic Wings logo in black. The interior Air-sole unit which is built into the heel of the rubber cupsole provides optimal support for quick moves on the court.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SE World Champs Black White
description: The Nike Dunk Low SE 'World Champ' embellishes the classic two-tone silhouette with decorations influenced by the world of professional wrestling. The low-top sneaker showcases a white leather base with black cracked leather overlays. The upper is accented by a black patent leather Nike Swoosh and embroidered Nike branding in metallic gold. A nod to a wrestling championship belt is found in the form of gold plated lace jewels while a black rubber outsole completes the look.

The Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Triple White' gives a new take of the legendary shoe design, updated in White and White. Its upper spotlights a leather base with overlays and the signature Wings’ Logo. On the upper, a Swoosh branding emphasizes the design with a nylon woven tongue. The midsole is built on top of a rubber outsole with a circular build for traction.

The Air Jordan 1 Low 'Green Toe' displays a new take of the legendary shoe design, renewed in Noble Green and Pollen. Its upper spotlights a leather base with overlays and the signature Jordan Wings’ Logo. On the upper, a Swoosh emphasizes the design with a breathable nylon tongue. The midsole is built on top of a rubber outsole with a circular build for traction.

The Yeezy Boost 350 V2 'Zyon' emerges with a stylized look on a neutral colorway. Built with Primeknit, the upper is bisected by a darker monofilament stripe, while the collar sports solid grey to add to the aesthetic. Underfoot, a semitranslucent rubber midsole overlays a full-length Boost midsole, giving way to a gum rubber outsole for traction.

Honoring the first of MJ's six NBA championship is the Air Jordan 6 Retro ‘Red Oreo.’ Maintaining its iconic look is the upper in white leather highlighted with airy perforations. Support and comfort are ensured with a clear rubber outsole and the heel's exposed Air-sole unit. Color is introduced via a speckled-white crimson on the heel tab and midsole as well as on the lace lock and tongue adorned with the Jumpman.

Featuring 'Fire Red'-style color-blocking, the Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Racer Blue' released in July 2021. The shoe's tumbled leather upper appears in white, highlighted by Racer Blue on the eyelets, collar and branding. The forefoot and heel elephant print overlays add a crackle effect, while underfoot, more Racer Blue accents the polyurethane midsole, which houses visible Air in the heel for cushioning.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Next Nature Sequoia
description: Made for colder weather in part of the 'Toasty' collection is the Nike Dunk Low Next Nature 'Sequoia.' A dark green hue permeates the upper, lined in fleece and featuring synthetic suede overlays on a quilted textile base made with 100% recycled polyester. Clashing orange accents are featured on the textured leather Swoosh and a heel tab marked with embroidered Nike branding. A pinwheel logo on the woven tongue tag is sustainably built that incorporates 20% recycled content by weight.

The sneaker that started it all emerges with a subdued palette on the Wmns Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Seafoam.' Released in August 2021, the shoe's upper is built entirely with leather, with the white base overlaid by Seafoam and complemented by Healing Orange on the laces. Perforations on the toe box are included for breathability, while underfoot, Air in the heel of the rubber cupsole provides cushioning. A concentric pattern on the rubber outsole offers traction.

A shoe made for the links is injected with familiar heritage details with the Air Jordan 12 Low Golf ‘Taxi.’ Honoring Michael Jordan’s fifth championship with the Bulls, the low-top golf shoe echoes the shoe he wore that season with overlays in black leather with lizard patterning against the white leather upper with characteristic stitching highlighted by gold eyelets. The Zoom Air unit in the midsole provides cushion and support while stability and grip is afforded by a hybrid outsole of traction patterning and seven removeable spikes.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Sun Club Multi (W)
description: A beloved basketball shoe gets an eco-friendly reinterpretation with the Nike women’s Dunk Low SE ‘Sun Club.’ The white textile base of the upper is layered with synthetic leather in lime green, pale blue, peach, coral and lavender hues and is constructed partly from recycled materials. The tropical vibe is reinforced with a smiley face accompanied by a palm tree on the lateral heel. The tongue tag declares ‘Nike Sun Club’ and is accented by bamboo-shaped lace dubrae.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 Patta Waves White
Nike Air Humara LX Jacquemus Ale Brown Gold (W)
description: The Jacquemus x Nike Air Humara LX ‘Brown’ treats Simon Porte Jacquemus’ favorite sneaker to a standout reinterpretation. Fuzzy suede overlays in beige layer on the brown upper with a mini-Swoosh in gold adorning the quarter panel. Cushion underfoot is ensured by the foam midsole wrapped in a houndstooth textile atop a rubber outsole with lugged pattern. Ribbon-like pink-and maroon eyelets add a pop of color and wrap around the heel. The heel tab and tongue are adorned with Jacquemus branding.

Celebrating Valentine's Day with frilly detailing and vibrant colors is the Nike women's Dunk Low 'Valentine's Day.' The low-top's upper is constructed from textile twill in a rich Team Red hue. Tumbled leather overlays at the forefoot and heel are rendered in Pink Prime, while the color-matched hairy suede Swoosh is trimmed in pleated, translucent lace. The same burgundy and fuchsia colors are seen again on the rubber cupsole.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 Light Madder Root Worn Blue
description: A Tinker Hatfield classic gets a color refresh with the Nike Air Max 1 ‘Light Madder Root.’ A creamy-tan base provides a neutral background for a distinctive Worn Blue overlay and coral mudguard and heel overlay, all in a soft suede. Stitched Nike Air Max branding appears at the heel. The tropical palette is completed with a Vivid Green signature Swoosh. Comfort and support are afforded by a PU midsole in off-white with a Max Air unit in pale green in the heel.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green Black
description: A two-tone look, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Pine Green 2.0' released in February 2020. The shoe's leather upper sports a mix of black leather and Pine Green tumbled leather, with Gym Red on the tongue tag. Underfoot, the Air-infused midsole offers the only contrast in white, giving way to a rubber outsole with a concentric traction pattern.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Skate Like a Girl
description: The founders of Skate Like a Girl, a female-founded nonprofit based in the Pacific Northwest, partnered with Nike to bring a new look and feel to the SB Dunk Low. A rich mix of materials, colors and artwork distinguish this skate shoe – a cream suede upper features overlays and a corduroy collar and tongue in violet, with a ridged scarlet Swoosh finishing the look. Branding includes Skate Like a Girl stitching on the tongue tag and linked-arm artwork by J Wu on the back heel. The shoe rides on a gum rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid Metallic Gold Black White
description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE 'Metallic Gold' is an elevated take on the basketball classic. The shoe's upper is built with leather, finished in white and black and highlighted by metallic gold overlays. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while underfoot, the midsole houses Air in the heel for cushioning. A black concentric rubber outsole is included for traction.

shoeName: Nike Tech Fleece Joggers Black/Dark Grey Heather/White
description:
Nike Tech Fleece is a Black/Dark Grey Heather/White colorway jogger made of breathable 100% cotton fabric.

The Nike Tech Fleece jogger is black with a dark grey heather volley short-like patch on the front. On it is a smaller white Nike logo on the left thigh. The jogger also features a ribbed waistband with a grey drawstring. It has a rib-knit cuff for a firmer grip on your leg. There are two inset side pockets. At the back is one back pocket patch fastened with a zipper.

Nike released the Tech Fleece joggers on 15th January 2022 with a retail price of $110.

The Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Alternate Bel-Air' draws from a 2013 Air Jordan colorway also inspired by the Fresh Prince of Bel-Air. The shoe's 90s-inspired look includes a white leather construction on the upper, with the inner lining sporting a vibrant print mismatched between the shoes. Further mismatched hits include the Jumpman and '23' branding, while underfoot, both shoes house visible Air for cushioning.

An earthy reinvention of a heritage running shoe distinguishes the Nike Air Max 95 NH ‘Ironstone.’ Underfoot, the PU midsole in dark brown features exposed Air-sole units in the heel and forefoot for lightweight cushioning. The upper consists of layers of undulating overlays in a gradient color palette in jacquard textile, blending from pale tan to brown. The webbing eyelets and stitched mini-Swoosh arrive in a subtle yellow.

shoeName: Nike Air Max 1 CLOT Kiss of Death (2021)
description: Bringing back a collaborative colorway from 2006, the CLOT x Air Max 1 ‘Kiss of Death’ 2021 released in 2021. The shoe’s upper features the same deconstructed tan suede upper as its predecessor, with transparent paneling on the toe box and a scaly Swoosh. Underfoot, a visible Max Air unit provides cushioning, giving way to a translucent rubber outsole that sports an updated multicolor reflexology-inspired graphic.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SE Teddy Bear Praline

description: Inspired by spacesuits, the Wmns Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Starfish' emerges with a unique construction. The shoe's upper features a black metallic mesh build, with raw edges revealing the Starfish underlays. Black mesh inserts appear at the quarter panel and vamp, with further Starfish on the tongue branding. Underfoot, visible Air in the heel of the midsole provides cushioning, giving way to a rubber outsole for traction.

colorway: Off-Noir/Brigade Blue-Dark Smoke Grey-Light Fusion Red
description: Released in August 2020, the Union LA x Air Jordan 4 Retro is a follow-up to an Air Jordan 1 collaboration from 2018. Built with black suede, the upper includes mesh on the toe box and collar. Translucent wings mark the quarter panel, while the classic eyelets appear in black and white. Contrast stitching emerges throughout, while the Air Jordan tongue tag sports an inside-out aesthetic. The side wall includes 'UN/LA' branding, while underfoot, a yellowed midsole contributes to the retro look, with visible Air in the heel providing cushioning.

When the Air Jordan 3 was released in 1988, it was the first Air Jordan to feature the elephant print, visible Air Unit and Jumpman logo, and was MJ’s first signature shoe designed by Tinker Hatfield. In 2018, to celebrate the 30th anniversary, the sneaker was re-released in its iconic ‘Black Cement’ colorway boasting the same trademark details—like the black tumbled leather upper—we all remember fondly.

Inspired by the 2015 colorway celebrating MJ's first NBA championship title is the Air Jordan 6 Retro GS ‘Chrome.’ A midsole with shots of metallic silver pairs with matching silver Jumpman branding adorning the back heel, sockliner and lace guard.
