The all-black upper in nubuck features ventilated underlays and an easy grip tongue and pull tab for busy kids on the go. Underfoot, support and traction are ensured with Air-sole cushioning and a clear outsole in grippy rubber.

shoeName: Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT Hare
description: The Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort ‘Hare’ takes its design cues from the classic Air Jordan 7, featuring a light grey suede upper and white leather heel and forefoot overlays. With nods to the legendary '90s Michael Jordan and Bugs Bunny ad campaign, this high-top delivers playful multicolor detailing, a cozy exposed foam collar and a Zoom Air tag. A Zoom Air unit is housed in the white rubber midsole houses for plush cushioning while the outsole blends Dark Concord EVA and crimson rubber for sturdy traction underfoot.

A classic favorite is given a refined makeover with the Nike women’s Dunk High ‘Fossil Stone.’ The upper appears in off-white leather intersected by a contrasting Swoosh in black and overlays in neutral beige. Comfort and a secure fit are ensured by the ventilated tongue with Nike branding and a collar in padded mesh. The high-top rides on a standard rubber cupsole for support underfoot.

The AJ9 was released during the legendary hoops star’s first retirement, the Air Jordan 9 Retro GS ‘Fire Red’ is a sleek rendition with subtle hits of color. The outsole in white rubber features imagery evoking MJ’s global prominence while the midsole in grey PU with an Air-sole unit in the heel provides cushioned comfort. White stitched leather on the upper is intersected by Cool Grey patent-leather overlays. The molded eyelets, Nike branding on the tongue tag with ‘Air Jordan’ and webbing pull tabs appear in Fire Red.

shoeName: Nike Air Griffey Max 1 San Francisco Giants
Nike Air Max BW OG Persian Violet (2021)
Nike Blazer Mid 77 Premium Certified Fresh

description: Arriving in May 2018, the women’s exclusive Air Max 270 ‘Barely Rose’ flaunts a two-tone mesh upper (with Elemental Rose) atop a crisp white midsole and Vintage Wine-colored exaggerated heel.

shoeName: Hoka One One Clifton 8 Eggnog Shifting Sand (W)
description:
The Hoka One One Clifton 8 Eggnog Shifting Sand W has become an addition to the Women's catalog that comes in a mix of Eggnog and Shifting Sand color scheme.

It features a mesh streamlined throughout the upper. Located on the side of the heel and on the tongue is the HOKA branding in an Eggnog color tone. The pull tab of the shoe is an extension of its collar, while the sole unit comprises an EVA foam midsole and a high-abrasive rubber outsole. Other detailing includes a geo pattern displayed on the outsoles.

The Hoka One One Clifton 8 Eggnog Shifting Sand W was released on August 13th, 2022. It retailed at $140.

shoeName: Nike Big Swoosh Reversible Boa Jacket (Asia Sizing) Gorge Green
Jordan 12 Retro Low Golf French Blue
description: In addition to his prowess on the court, MJ is also known for his love of golf. The Air Jordan 12 Low Golf ‘French Blue’ brings a golf makeover to a classic favorite. The upper in white tumbled leather and radiating stitching is the base for reptile-textured French Blue overlays. The vivid blue repeats on the tongue's stitched Jumpman and heel tab branding. The midsole in foam is enhanced by a full-length Zoom Air unit, while a translucent outsole modified with removeable golf spikes completes the look and also provides traction via its herringbone patterning.

shoeName: Nike Zoom GT Cut 2 Sabrina Ionescu Takeover Mode
Travis Scott x Jordan Paisley Shorts Orewood
description:
The Travis Scott x Jordan Paisley Shorts Orewood comprises of Paisley pattern style make.

This collaborative garment between American musician and Nike is made of a blend of cotton and polyester materials and features a contrast of black on its hems. The Paisley Shorts also have a ribbed waist, with multiple stitches. Additionally, an adjustable drawstring cords on its waist for fitting. The design is completed with paisley graphic and a black Jumpman logo near the waist and on its thighs.

The Travis Scott x Jordan Paisley Shorts Orewood debuted in the market on December 15th, 2022, and retailed at $105.

shoeName: Nike Air VaporMax Plus Black Metallic Gold
description: The Air VaporMax Plus 'Black Gold' brings an elevated colorway to its hybrid performance construction. Drawing from the Air Max Plus, the upper features a stretch textile construction in black overlaid by a tonal TPU cage. Metallic gold highlights the tongue and branding, matched underfoot by the VaporMax unit, which provides cushioning. A shank plate completes the look while providing stability.

shoeName: Nike Dunk High Retro Reverse Goldenrod
New Balance 2002R The Basement Stone Grey
Jordan Nu Retro 1 Low Varsity Red Black
description: First debuting in 2002, this Jordan Nu Retro 1 Low ‘Chicago’ returns for it s 20th anniversary. Characterized by the signature colors of the Chicago Bulls, the upper combines Varsity Red and black leather with white panels adorned by an exaggerated Wings logo. The midsole is color-blocked in white and red and features interior Air-sole cushioning and Jumpman branding, while the Air Jordan I rubber outsole returns to supply support and grip.

shoeName: adidas Adizero Prime X Off White Pulse Lilac
Nike ZoomX Vaporfly Next% 2 Coconut Milk Ghost Green Bright Crimson
adidas Gazelle Indoor Blue Fusion Gum (W)
Nike Air Force 1 Low SP AMBUSH Phantom
Nike Air Force 1 Low Valentine's Day (2023) (GS)
adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Stone Sage
description: The adidas Yeezy Foam Runner 'Stone Sage' showcases a slight marbleized print across a beige hue. As with all Foam Runners, a one-piece build is crafted with injected EVA foam, sculpted for comfort as there are several cored out holes for ventilation and breathability. A textured footbed offers a comfortable fit, while a wavy traction pattern offers grip.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro Paisley Brown
description: An iconic skate favorite gets a bohemian makeover with the Nike Dunk Low Pro Premium SB ‘Paisley.’ Built on a gum rubber outsole, the textile upper is flooded with an allover paisley print in green, blue, pink and brown. Brown piping in leather will dissolve over time to reveal off-white suede in its place. The signatures Swoosh appears in white while ‘Nike’ appears on the leather heel tab in brown.

Dressing the retro hoops shoe in a refined two-tone color scheme is the Nike women's Dunk Low 'Harvest Moon.' The leather upper combines a clean white base with contrasting overlays in a subtle peach beige hue. It has standard Dunk features such as a perforated toe box, breathable nylon tongue, and embroidered Nike branding on the back tab. Underneath is a rubber cupsole with white sidewalls and a beige rubber outsole.

The Day of the Dead is commemorated with a distinctive reinterpretation in the Nike Dunk Low ‘SiEMPRE Familia.’ The upper delivers a rich mix of materials and colors, including reptile-patterned leather on the upper in chameleon green and a blue, red and orange-patterned Swoosh. The vibrant colors of the upper are supported on a white midsole and a clear rubber outsole. Adorning the lateral heel is an iguana in vivid yellow with a red gem for an eye. ‘SiEMPRE Familia’ appears on the left sockliner, emphasizing the holiday's themes of family and community.

The unique construction of the Yeezy 450 features a blacked-out look on the Yeezy 450 'Dark Slate.' Also lacking exterior branding, the shoe's knit upper appears in black, with an integrated lacing system and elastic, sock-like cuff supporting the fit. Underfoot, the tooling forgoes a traditional midsole, instead sporting a rubber outsole that climbs up the heel and side wall, offering both traction down below and support up top.

shoeName: Nike Zoom Cortez SP sacai White University Red Blue
Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Black Lime Ice
description: The Air Max 90 Terrascape ‘Black Lime Ice’ celebrates a heritage classic with updated, eco-friendly features. Overlays in black synthetic suede appear on the charcoal ripstop upper while clear TPU eyelets secure the laces. Additional ease of wear is provided by webbing pull tabs, while branding is featured on the tongue and heel with a speckled Crater Foam Swoosh and patch. The midsole in the same material is wrapped in a clear cage atop a grippy rubber outsole made partly with Nike Grind.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Essential Paisley Pack Barley (W)

description:
The Nike KD 14 Aunt Pearl are high tops and typically fall at the top of the ankle for most wearers. They also have extra cushioning, making them comfortable for longer walks.

The Nike KD 14 Aunt Pearl has a Gum rubber outsole, as well as a vibrant pink base that features a detailed pattern. Towards the front of the shoe, you will find a hot pink speckled pattern. Across the pink laces and tongue, there is a pink strap that features the iconic Nike Swoosh symbol.

First released in April of 2022, the Nike KD 14 Aunt Pearl had a starting retail price of $150.

shoeName: Nike LD Waffle sacai CLOT Kiss of Death Net Orange Blaze
description: Nike brings you a triple collaboration in the sacai x Clot x Nike LDWaffle 'Net Orange Blaze'. Drawing from the CLOT x Nike Air Max 1 'Kiss of Death,' it combines features from the LDV and Waffle Racer. With a tan semi-translucent textile upper paired with tonal suede overlays at the forefoot and heel. The signature double Swooshes from sacai are brick red and orange leather with a slight snakeskin exterior. Subtle lime green color slashes the double-stacked eyestay, triple-branded heel tab, and the dual woven tags on top of the tongue. Grip down the street with waffle-traction and a two-tone midsole with an elongated heel.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High White Black Volt University Gold
description: Inspired by various Air Jordan 1 colorways, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Volt Gold' features vibrant accents. The shoe's leather upper appears primarily in white, with University Gold on the heel and Volt on the collar overlay. Black throughout provides contrast, while the exposed-foam tongue includes a reversed translucent tag. An off-white Air midsole offers cushioning, with a black concentric rubber outsole providing traction.

shoeName: Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki
description: A follow-up to a 2019 collaboration, the Travis Scott x Air Jordan 6 Retro 'British Khaki' released with the help of the Houston rapper. Built with a mix of suede and canvas, the shoe's upper appears in British Khaki, highlighted by Bright Crimson on the heel pull-loop and tongue branding. The lateral collar includes a stash pouch, with the medial side sporting zippered detailing. The heels include mismatched Air and Cactus Jack branding, and underfoot, the usual visible Air in the heel provides cushioning.

The Air Jordan 5 Retro GS ‘Green Bean’ brings back a colorway known for nearly two decades. The leather upper in trademark grey has a modern, reflective finish, and vivid green details embellish the collar lining and Jumpman logo at the tongue and heel. The dark grey polyurethane midsole provides lightweight cushioning alongside a visible Air-sole heel unit and shark tooth detailing, another 'Green Bean' accent. The outsole in translucent herringbone-tread rubber outsole provides superior grip and traction.

The properties of water and how it interacts with light serves as the inspiration for the Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Ocean.’ The aquatic theme is echoed on the clear rubber outsole with blue-patterned swirls. The white leather base on the upper features Bright Spruce overlays and a cushy low-cut collar and airy mesh tongue for comfort and a secure fit.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low VD Valentine's Day (2022) (W)
Jordan 1 Retro High Tokyo Bio Hack
description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Tokyo Bio Hack' features inspiration from the Japanese capital. The shoe's upper is built with a mix of leather and suede, finished in a color-blocked look that brings to mind Undefeated's Nike Dunk High NL collaboration from 2005. Underfoot, the painted Air midsole provides cushioning, giving way to a concentric outsole for traction.

The first silhouette in Nike’s Air Max family to featuring cushioning specifically developed for lifestyle, the Air Max 270 shows off an essential black and white colorway. The shoe’s signature large-volume 270-degree Max Air unit is finished in black, matched by a breathable mesh upper with contrasting white hits on the shoe’s branding elements.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W are women-sized ankle boots that feature a suede upper and are available in an antelope brown color.

The Ultra Mini boots by UGG are designed with a brown suede upper crafted from sheepskin. The sheepskin suede upper is lightweight, and the thick and fluffy interior is made for warmth. Underfoot, the slip-in style classic ankle boots sit on a rubber outsole that rounds off the design.

The UGG Classic Ultra Mini Antilope W was originally released on the 1st of November 2021. The retail price was set at $140.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Shattered Backboard
Jordan 7 Retro  Trophy Room New Sheriff in Town
description: Jordan Brand and Trophy Room collaborate on the AJ7, celebrating the 30th anniversary of the 'Dream Team'. The Air Jordan 7 Retro 'New Sheriff in Town' takes a Team USA inspired color palette, featuring a deep red suede base with off white overlays and a navy neoprene tongue. A multi-color heel tab references the Olympic Rings, while a Trophy Room logo and #9 on the back heel symbolize the gold medals from the Dream Team championship run. The midsole and outsole feature red, white and blue with gold accents, similar to the regular AJ7 'Olympic' colorway. Additional details on this Trophy Room edition are MJ's signature etched across the lateral heel area, along with 'New Sheriff in Town' on the inside tongue tags - a nod to a quote that MJ said to Magic Johnson and Larry Bird at a team scrimmage.

Raw edges and a disheveled build characterize the New Balance 2002R ‘Pink,’ which releases as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack.’ The 860v2 inspired the pre-distressed midsole which features ABZORB cushioning and shock-absorbing N-ergy technology in the heel. Brilliant pinks and lavender infuse the upper in ventilated mesh while ragged suede overlays embellish the quarter panel, heel overlay and forefoot.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Retro High Fearless UNC Chicago
description: Dropping in 2019 as part of Jordan Brand’s ‘Fearless Ones’ collection, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Fearless' features a distinctive color scheme that draws inspiration from the first three patent leather colorways of the iconic silhouette. The high-top’s crisp white upper is accented with Gym Red overlays on the forefoot, University Blue on the heel and a blend of black and gold on the jeweled Wings logo.

The Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Shattered Backboard' brings a classic Jordan Brand look to a different classic silhouette. Drawing from the Air Jordan 1 colorway, the shoe's upper emerges with a white leather base on the upper, sporting textile mesh on the collar, throat and quarter panel, with the latter replacing the usual netting. The reflective silver tongue includes Total Orange Jumpman branding, matched underfoot by the polyurethane midsole, which includes visible Air in the heel for cushioning. A herringbone rubber outsole offers traction.

Originally released in 2010 for a Christmas Day collection, the Zoom Kobe 6 Protro 'Grinch' dropped in December 2020. The shoe's upper features a Green Apple and Volt look, with polyurethane detailing creating a snakeskin-style texture throughout the construction. Crimson on the branding and laces adds to the holiday aesthetic, while underfoot, the midsole incorporates Zoom Air to provide cushioning.

Giving the nod to the Georgetown Hoyas, the Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Georgetown' emerges in the school's mix of hues. The shoe's tumbled leather upper appears in Midnight Navy, with grey on the eyestay, tongue and collar complementing the design. More grey marks the elephant print overlays at the toe and heel, while underfoot, visible Air in the heel of the polyurethane midsole provides cushioning.

shoeName: Nike Vaporwaffle sacai Sesame Blue Void
description: Made in collaboration with Chitose Abe's Tokyo fashion label, the sacai x VaporWaffle 'Sesame Blue Void' emerges with retro and modern inspiration. Drawing from the 1983 Pegasus and the VaporFly, the shoe's hybrid construction is built with textile on the upper, overlaid by leather and suede and finished in neutral tones. Blue Void marks one of the Swooshes and the heel patch, while two tongues add to the double aesthetic. Underfoot, a layered foam midsole provides cushioning, split at the heel, giving way to a waffle rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Low SE Dark Beetroot Roma Green (GS)
Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit Ekiden
silhoutte: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit
make: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% Flyknit

shoeName: Nike Air VaporMax Plus SE Black (W)
Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2 Platinum Tint Hyper Pink (W)
Nike Air Max 97 OG Silver Bullet (2022) (W)
New Balance 990v3 Patta Keep Your Family Close
description: Constructed on an ENCAP midsole with speckled midsole, the Patta x New Balance 990v3 Made in USA ‘Keep Your Family Close’ is a new take on a signature lifestyle runner, and made in sizes for the whole family. The pale green mesh and suede upper with airy overlays in neon green includes branding that salutes NB and the Netherlands retailer; 'Patta' appears on the lateral heel, the 'N' appears in silver and a Patta logo decorates the heel.

shoeName: New Balance 2002R The Basement Moss Green
description: The Basement x New Balance 2002R ‘Moss Green’ features a tonal mix of green and olive in waterproof heavy suede and textured rubber with contrasting black toe caps and mudguard. The tongue and back heel deliver BSMT salutes while Basement’s ‘9 Bar’ logo appears against the ’N’ logo in white leather. Underfoot, cushion is ensured by an ABZORB midsole in a contrasting black.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Low Reflective Swoosh White Blue
Nike Tech Fleece Full-Zip Hoodie Light Bone/Black
Nike Dunk Low Ocean Bliss Citron Tint (W)
Nike Dunk Low LX Black Team Gold (W)

description: The Nike women’s Dunk High ‘Pink Prime’ takes a clean and simple hoops silhouette and injects it with eye-popping color. The upper in white with overlays in vibrant hot pink features perforations on the toe box for ventilation and a comfy leather collar lined with mesh. Underfoot, the high-top rides on a traditional cupsole in white rubber with matching sidewalls atop a rubber outsole in pink.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid SE Coconut Milk Particle Grey
description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE 'Coconut Milk Particle Grey' gives a new iteration of the iconic sneaker design, redesigned in Coconut Milk and Coconut Milk. Its upper spotlights a leather base with overlays and the standard Wings’ Logo. On the upper, a Swoosh emphasizes the design with a breathable nylon tongue. The Air-sole is built on top of a rubber outsole with a circular build for traction.

shoeName: adidas Yeezy Foam RNR Desert Sand
description: Crafted from injected EVA foam that is molded and sculpted into one overall piece that forms the shoe, the Yeezy Foam Runner is a design and engineering marvel. A light Desert Sand hue envelopes the entire slip-on, including the herringbone traction pattern on the outsole and the smooth and detailed upper.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Pale Coral (W)
description: Made with 20% of recycled content by weight is the Nike women's Dunk Low Next Nature 'Pale Coral.' The upper is synthetic leather with a crisp white base and contrasting overlays in a soft pink hue. Neon is featured on the Volt-colored sockliner with Nike's pinwheel logo stamped on the heel. The low-top is built on a standard rubber cupsole that's paired with white sidewalls and a light grey rubber outsole.

The Yeezy Boost 700 arrives in an unmissable colorway, showcasing a vibrant Hi-Res Red on the mesh and leather upper portion of the lifestyle runner. Black suede overlays that run across the shoe are reminiscent of the original release, including the green pop on the front of the midsole and the grey toe cap. Full-length Boost cushioning is embedded in the sculpted midsole, highlighted with red and orange accents. A rubber Hi-Res Red herringbone outsole completes the look.

Originally worn by Michael Jordan at the 1996 NBA All-Star Game, the Air Jordan 11 Low Retro 'Legend Blue' emerges in low-top fashion with this April 2021 release. Built with leather, the shoe's upper appears in white, bolstered by a tonal patent leather mudguard and sporting ballistic mesh on the tongue. Legend Blue accents the heel branding, while the 25th anniversary of the shoe gets a callout on the sockliner.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid White Black Racer Blue
description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Racer Blue' emerges with OG-style color-blocking on this 2021 release. Built with leather, the shoe's upper sports a white base, with the overlays contrasting the look in black. Suede marks the collar, which appears in Racer Blue, matched by the branding, including the leather Swoosh on the side wall. Underfoot, Air in the heel of the rubber midsole provides cushioning, with the outsole incorporating a concentric pattern for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Stussy Light Bone Black
description: A classic mid-top gets a refined reinvention with the Stussy x Nike Air Force 1 Mid ‘Black White.’ The crisp white upper is complemented by overlays in black repeated on the signature Swoosh. Dual branding decorates the tongue tag, Stussy’s double-S logo adorns the heel tab, and ‘Stussy’ appears on the ankle strap, which is adjustable for a secure fit. Additional SS branding appears as perforations on the toe box. A standard rubber cupsole supports the build underfoot and pairs with white sidewalls atop a rubber outsole in black with traction patterning for optimal grip.

Making over the iconic silhouette with a tan textile upper and tonal suede overlays is the Union LA x Air Jordan 2 Retro SP 'Rattan.' An amber underlay is revealed through perforated detailing on the quarter panel that matches the molded eyelets and an attached 'UN/LA' tag. A woven Jumpman tag is featured on the exposed foam tongue with an embossed Nike wordmark on the heel tab. Decorating the woven tag on the lateral collar is a retro Wings logo with a cream-colored polyurethane midsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning on underneath. The Union x Jordan 2 'Rattan' will drop on April 15, 2022.

The Nike Lebron 20 Time Machine is a multi-toned sneaker that features medium soft pink and barely green hues as the dominant color schemes.

The woven mesh upper of this Lebron 20 from Nike is contrasted by the fuchsia-colored padded collar that is complemented by a orange hue stitching on the leather eyestay. The lateral side features a turquoise Swoosh with exposed deco stitching encircling it, placed above an iridescent Swoosh. The sneaker also has a guardrail coated in synthetic material and decorated with a design that holds the lateral forefoot in place.

The Nike Lebron 20 Time Machine debuted on September 29th, 2022, with a retail price of $200.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid SE Pastel Vivid Green Grind (GS)

description: In collaboration with designer Justin Saunders in the third iteration of the vaunted 990 series is the JJJJound x New Balance 990v3 Made in USA 'Olive.' The upper is made from breathable mesh with soft pigskin suede overlays and is permeated with rich olive green hues. A black 'N' logo is featured on the quarter panel, while 'JJJJound' is inscribed on the reflective silver heel tab. It's built on New Balance's ENCAP midsole with a plush EVA core and a polyurethane rim.

A heritage favorite from 1985 is treated to a tie-dye palette with the Air Jordan 1 Low SE ‘Tie Dye.’ Traditional ‘Black Toe’ color blocking forms the backdrop, with a white base and overlays at the forefoot and Swoosh in black. The heel overlay reveals a tie-die pattern that alternates from aqua on the left to lavender on the right, both accompanied by embroidered Wings branding. The rubber outsole is delivered in vivid lavender and provides sturdy traction underfoot.

shoeName: Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex Light Curry
description: A shoe ready for the elements, the Air Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex ‘Light Curry’ pairs water resistance with a rich mix of materials and hues. Ripstop textile in off-white dresses the upper and is paired with light orange overlays in nubuck. The sneaker is lined with Gore-Tex for protection against wet and cold. The signature Swoosh is reflective for darker runs and the lateral heel is adorned with ‘Gore-Tex’ branding. Comfort and support underfoot are supplied by a traditional AJ1 cupsole with an Air-sole heel unit housed in a comfy PU wedge.

The Air Jordan 4 Retro GS 'University Blue' is a grade-school shoe with a familiar University of North Carolina colorway. As a result, the shoe's upper includes a woven jock tag on the tongue, with the look recalling the labels on throwback Nike basketball jerseys. Otherwise finished primarily in University Blue, the upper includes cement detailing throughout, matched by the midsole underfoot, which houses visible Air in the heel for cushioning.

The Yeezy Boost 700 V2 'Vanta' emerges with a blacked-out look with this June 2019 release. The shoe's upper is built with multilayer mesh, overlaid by suede, all finished tonally. The sleek upper is supported underfoot by a bulky midsole that houses a full-length Boost unit for cushioning, giving way to a rubber outsole that provides traction.

This mid-top silhouette reimagines the iconic 1999 low-top colorway. Air Jordan 14 Retro ‘Ginger’ features an upper in a rich shade of ginger contrasting with the white toebox and midsole. Exaggerated '23' and Jumpman branding adorn the heel overlay in black rubber. Additional branding decorates the outsole, with a Jumpman in white on the left shoe and 'XIV' in ginger on the right. Traction and grip are ensured with a Phyon midsole with Zoom Air cushioning and tire-tread inspired herringbone traction.

Inspired by Michael Jordan's 63-point game at the Boston Garden during the 1986 playoffs, the Wmns Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Lucky Green' emerges with a Boston Celtics-style colorway. The shoe's upper features a white leather base overlaid by Lucky Green leather sporting raw edges, with red on the 'Wings' logo. Underfoot, Air in the midsole provides cushioning, giving way to a concentric outsole for traction.

The Wmns Dunk Low 'Green Glow' emerges with a vibrant look on its classically color-blocked design. The shoe's upper features an entirely leather construction, finished with a white base that's highlighted by the overlays, which appear in Green Glow. More Green Glow marks the Swoosh branding, matched by the woven tongue tag. Perforations on the toe box are included for breathability, while underfoot, both colors come together on the rubber cupsole.

Inspired by the December’s most infamous character, the adidas Forum Low ‘Grinch’ gives this low-top a makeover befitting the beloved anti-hero. In an array of shades of vivid green, the upper in fuzzy suede includes a matching ankle strap. The tongue tags are adorned with the trademark Trefoil on the right and the Grinch’s unmistakable eyes on the left. The sockliners features the character’s portrait, smiling on the right and grimacing on the left. Underfoot, support and comfort arrive via a neon green rubber cupsole.

Released in April 2021, the Air Jordan 5 Retro GS 'Raging Bull' 2021 brings back one half of the 2009 Raging Bull pack. Emerging in grade-school sizing, the shoe's suede upper appears in Varsity Red, with the signature quarter panel netting marking the side wall. Black contrast throughout, including on the molded eyelets, completes the familiar 'Bred' look, with reflective silver detailing highlighting the tongue. Underfoot, the midsole houses visible Air in the heel for cushioning.

A heritage classic combines details from its 1985 original with an eye-catching colorway in the women’s Air Jordan 1 Mid SE ‘University Red Pomegranate.’ The smooth leather base features shiny overlays in synthetic leather, all in a brilliant crimson hue. True to the ‘80s version of the AJ High is this pair’s toe box with airy perforations and Wings branding on the lateral collar flap. Underfoot, a traditional rubber cupsole features an Air-sole unit for lightweight cushioning.

Jordan Brand teamed up with Virgil Abloh's luxury streetwear label to create the Off-White x Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Fire Red' in October 2020. A follow-up to an early 2020 Air Jordan 5 collaboration, the shoe's upper features an off-white textile construction, with the midfoot, collar and reflective silver tongue sporting circular cutouts. Helvetica text marks the medial side, while underfoot, a contrasting black midsole houses Air in the heel for cushioning. A pre-yellowed finish on the outsole, which provides traction, completes the look.

The ACG Air Max Goadome 'Triple Black' combines a rugged winter boot aesthetic with Nike Air Max cushioning. The 3/4 high-top silhouette features a waterproof black leather upper with a cushioned perforated collar for comfortable support. A matching black midsole, fitted with a visible Max Air unit, is supported underfoot by a durable All-Trac rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk High Next Nature Summit White (W)
description: Giving the classic silhouette a winter-ready makeover is the Nike women's Dunk High LX 'Toasty.' The shoe is made with 20% recycled content by weight and features a quilted textile upper in mismatched panels of white, brown, green, and tan, with a black synthetic suede Swoosh. A crimson suede heel tab gives a bold pop of color. Nike's pinwheel tongue tag references the shoe's sustainable build, while the sockliner features Toasty branding in a nod to the warm fleece that lines the interior.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Mid SE All-Star Carbon Fiber (2021) (GS)
description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE GS 'All-Star 2021' is a grade-school iteration of the shoe. Paying tribute to the NBA's exhibition showcase, the shoe emerges with a classic colorway and an elevated construction. Built with a white leather base, the upper is contrasted by black patent leather overlays, with a faux carbon-fiber print marking the Swoosh, heel and collar. Perforations on the tongue tag provide breathability, while underfoot, Air in the heel of the midsole provides cushioning.

shoeName: Jordan 1 Low Black Dark Powder Blue (W)
description: The women’s Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG ‘Black Dark Powder Blue’ dresses the classic silhouette in a familiar color combination that nods to Michael Jordan’s time at North Carolina. The low-top dons a leather upper that contrasts a stark white base with forefoot and heel overlays in black and powder blue. A woven Nike tag embellishes the breathable nylon tongue, while an embroidered Wings logo decorates the heel tab. A sturdy rubber cupsole packs an encapsulated Air-sole unit in the heel for lightweight cushioning.

The Nike Dunk High Retro 'Lakers' drapes the classic hoops silhouette in the signature purple and gold of the storied Los Angeles team. Showcasing a color blocking similar to the 'Be True to Your School' look from the original 1985 release, the all-leather upper features Court Purple overlays on top of University Gold. A crisp white midsole adds bold contrast, while a purple hued outsole completes the look.

The women’s Air Jordan 3 Retro ‘Black Gold’ reimagines this classic silhouette. The iconic elephant print overlays at the forefront and heel adorn the black tumbled leather upper. A metallic sunflower gold adorns tongue, eyestay and collar. Gym Red Jumpman branding is featured on the tongue and against the black heel tab. Comfort and traction are delivered via a clear rubber outsole.
